see: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=34oOp1OLOUk
first installation: Go, Git, toroisehg


C:\>cd go
C:\Go>mkdir projects
C:\Go>set "GOPATH=C:\Go\projects"
C:\Go>cd %gopath%
C:\Go\projects>go get github.com/influxdata/influxdb
C:\Go\projects>cd src\github.com\influxdata\influxdb
C:\Go\projects\src\github.com\influxdata\influxdb>go get -u -f ./...
C:\Go\projects\src\github.com\influxdata\influxdb>cd %gopath%\bin
C:\Go\projects\bin>influxd config > influxdb.generated.conf
C:\Go\projects\bin>copy influxdb.generated.conf influxdb.conf
  1 file(s) copied.
C:\Go\projects\bin>start wordpad influxdb.conf
C:\Go\projects\bin>influxd -config influxdb.conf

configuration file:
C:\Go\projects\bin>start wordpad influxdb.conf

startcommand for influxdb:
C:\Go\projects\bin>influxd -config influxdb.conf
